Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.54,0:00:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people seek\Nthe answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future--\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright, but I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.54,0:00:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.15,0:00:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really, really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.99,0:01:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.14,0:01:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.58,0:01:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really need\Neverything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.36,0:01:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.27,0:01:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Broggy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.81,0:02:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then! Accelerate, Candle Service!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.58,0:02:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn these people into wax figures!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.72,0:02:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hands won't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna die this way!\NCan't we do something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.40,0:02:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whadya say we crush\Nthese guys together?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.94,0:02:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight alongside you\Nand your fighting spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.91,0:02:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!\NWhat can you possibly do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kick your asses,\Njust so you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.96,0:02:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys spoiled\Nthe old giant guys' duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Broggy!\NWe've taken on your frustration!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, could you bust\Nthis pillar for us, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.71,0:03:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Break the pillar, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Hex on Luffy! Colors Trap"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.88,0:03:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm gonna be solidified,\NI prefer this pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.69,0:03:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be playing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, do something about your leg!\NIt's painful just looking at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then quit looking at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.47,0:04:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the idiot who suggested\Ncutting our legs off in this situation
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we could escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That ain't true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was gonna cut 'em off\Nso we could fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's even stupider! Get serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.38,0:04:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! You have no common sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still haven't even escaped\Nfrom this situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.46,0:04:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yet neither of them seems\Nto sense the danger at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, runt. Is that all\Nthe struggling you got?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.74,0:04:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Looks like it's\Nsomeone else's turn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.11,0:04:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 3. Those people don't\Nseem concerned at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could say the same about you,\NMiss Golden Week!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.22,0:04:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Urgh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. If you're gonna do a pose,\Nnow's your chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put me on your level.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Bushido! Please be\Nmore serious about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More like stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Like you're one to talk!\N--It seems we're being mocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is truly displeasing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since he showed up, they've been--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hardly seems to be\Nthat reliable of a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll finish him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.99,0:05:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finish him off?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He showed up here alive and well\Nbecause your attacks don't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, he's at a level\Nthat's too much for you to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two can take care of the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:06:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll add Straw Hat Luffy\Nto my wax figure collection...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.46,0:06:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are too damn annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.36,0:06:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gone a bit too far!\NGive yourselves up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Small fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Preparations are complete!\NWe got your back, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Candle Lock!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy-san!\N--Damn. He's already gotten caught?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.90,0:06:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? It's heavy, like a mallet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now for your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,0:07:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! This is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.68,0:07:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Candle Lock!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old giant guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to bother you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What's he up to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.38,0:07:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Mallet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky! The mallet on my legs broke, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We survived...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That didn't help things at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, that was dangerous!\NWhy didn't you guys run?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.50,0:08:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't move! Isn't it obvious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.88,0:08:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you guys told me to break the pillar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.05,0:08:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really a good idea to put our\Nlives in his hands, Mr. Bushido?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me.\NThat's the only choice we got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus it looks like my arms are stuck now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be serious about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on... It feels like my body\Nis hardening more and more now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move at all now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fools! With the candles closer,\Nyour hardening has sped up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can become\Nwax figures even quicker!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy thinks he can act\Nall smug and arrogant!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.06,0:09:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You guys are gonna be wax figures?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we've been trying to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.94,0:09:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just destroy this set, Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I won't let you interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wax-Wax Arts! Harpoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exploding Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.87,0:10:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was rather bland.\NYou don't use very good gunpowder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He ate the Exploding Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. It really is fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Good thing I posed beforehand.\N--You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san! Please, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! That pumpkin's\Nthe bad thing, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on! Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Candle Wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.47,0:10:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.14,0:10:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be my line.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:11:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd appreciate it if you didn't\Ninterfere with my creative activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Candle Lock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.82,0:11:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a mallet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.53,0:11:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Candle Wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Mallet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.18,0:11:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray! Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Mr. 3...\N--Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Hurry and break this\Nset while there's still time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--No.\N--Quit joking around and hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be acting stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel like saving you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colors Trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time! Do something\Nabout this thing already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:13:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Then hurry!\N--Yeah, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't feel like saving you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you keep saying that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the ones who're\Nabout to be wax figures!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.12,0:13:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?! We're about to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.39,0:13:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But for some reason,\NI just can't get motivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.76,0:13:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a motivation problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dammit! What's happened to him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our friends're gonna die\Nif he doesn't hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring him back to his senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Karoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-When did you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up. He's already\Nfallen into a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. See where he's standing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where he's standing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.76,0:13:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?\NThere's a strange black pattern...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so important about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. It's nothing.\NIt's just paint.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paint?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.51,0:14:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,\Nboth you and them are goners!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karoo! Let's just run for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's planning to escape on the bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.81,0:14:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sprint at full speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Wait!\NI haven't gotten on yet! Karoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.49,0:15:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Alright! Stop! Let me get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point in being scared of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.58,0:15:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Golden Week!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colors Trap: Betrayal Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.29,0:15:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touch the black paint,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.13,0:15:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you'll want to betray your friends,\Nno matter what they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.03,0:15:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does she mean?!\NWhat happened?! Explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.47,0:15:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a "realist painter" who can\Neven create real colors of emotion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her refined sense of color\Ncan manipulate people's minds
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.81,0:15:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,through the use of her paints.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:16:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Manipulate?! That's not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.12,0:16:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That simpleminded idiot is\Nalready easy enough to manipulate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then doesn't he just need\Nto get away from that paint?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Get away from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san! Whatever you do,\Ndo not move from that black circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.11,0:16:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want you to save us at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.85,0:16:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made him do the exact\Nopposite of what you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was kind of weird just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.26,0:16:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I'll save you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But never mind you guys!\NI just wanna laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Why?!\N--Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.12,0:17:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colors Trap: Laughter Yellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know you're not supposed to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's on his clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Hurry and take off that clothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Never mind that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just feel like laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it keeps raining down at this pace,\Nwe won't last one more minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you guys come here to play?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.77,0:18:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! When Usopp ran into him,\Nthe paint on his back smudged!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.58,0:18:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I wind up doing something again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.18,0:18:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Knock it off, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was Laughter Yellow funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Are you stupid?! Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.29,0:18:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, I gotta break that pumpkin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.63,0:18:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colors Trap: Bullfight Red.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you aiming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not allowed to break it!\NYou'll make Mr. 3 angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as bulls rush at red capes,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you feel the urge to attack\Nthat Bullfight Red mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand you anymore!\NGet out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:18:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't his kind of fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All his power is useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now to finish it with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll mix the Laughter Yellow on\Nyour back with Sadness Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.84,0:19:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colors Trap: Tranquil Green!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such nice tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.02,0:19:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... What happens now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? I told you you should've posed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you still be so calm about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.88,0:19:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, they run away fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nose Fancy Double Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You missed! Way to go, Karoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Special Attack: Lead Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta go back to Luffy\Nand the others again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting nowhere,\Nchasing them all around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.01,0:20:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to use it\Non such small fries,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's no dodging this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A .44-caliber,\Nsix-shot flintlock revolver.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new South Blue model.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can fire continuously,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and if I use it, the bullets are invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.87,0:20:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy's acting that way because of\Nthat paint the bad guys mentioned!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:20:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're related somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.05,0:21:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was also some on his back\Nwhen I crashed into him earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.39,0:21:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can just do something\Nabout the paint...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh. Such nice tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.02,0:21:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.02,0:21:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.29,0:21:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such... nice... tea...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.77,0:21:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, you idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.77,0:21:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is awfully big
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.24,0:22:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so even if there is treasure somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the odds are astronomical
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.95,0:22:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So relying on dumb luck\Nwon't get you anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.09,0:22:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So even...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.89,0:22:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if someone stops me or\Nlaughs at me from the shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.63,0:22:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the ship will continue forward
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.84,0:22:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.24,0:22:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'm a fool, but I gotta go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crazier the dream,\Nthe cooler the ambition
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.62,0:22:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'm a fool, but I'm gonna fight
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.29,0:22:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The farther the sea,\Nthe more heavenly it surely is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.30,0:23:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do everything you can, and you'll\Nget a little nearer to any horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.51,0:23:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! They've only just hardened!\NThere's still time to save them!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.32,0:23:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Really?!\N--We're gonna save you now, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Karoo! Run around!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.45,0:23:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to let anyone else die!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.39,0:23:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It'll be hot, but endure it!\N--Wake up, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.59,0:23:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's damn strange.\NWhy hasn't anyone come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.73,0:23:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.10,0:23:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Time to Fight Back!\NUsopp's Quick Thinking and Fire Star!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.27,0:23:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
